### Worker health (Nest → Python proxy check)
GET {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/health
Accept: application/json

###

### List disposable domains
GET {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/domains
Accept: application/json

###

### Create mailbox (random address)
# @name createMailbox
POST {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{}

###

### Create mailbox (custom local + domain)
POST {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "localPart": "john.test",
  "domain": "virgilian.com"
}

###

@newMailboxId = {{createMailbox.response.body.id}}

### Get mailbox — use @newMailboxId or set mailboxId in http-client.env.json
GET {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes/{{newMailboxId}}
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes/{{mailboxId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes/{{newMailboxId}}/messages
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes/{{mailboxId}}/messages
Accept: application/json

###

### Get message detail (set messageId from list response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes/{{mailboxId}}/messages/{{messageId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete mailbox
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/temp-mail/mailboxes/{{mailboxId}}
Accept: application/json
